oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Imperials Newsletter (page 2)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Imperials (Musical group); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative framed by a masking sheet containing the second page of the Imperials News Letter. The newsletter contains three columns; the first lists the Imperials' tour dates for February and March. The second column, "Haleyville Hess Day," describes the Imperials' concert at the Haleyville High School in Haleyville, Alabama, the hometown of Jake Hess. The third column contains the Bible verse Phillippians 3:13-14. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
